parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the intake manifold gasket can cause coolant to leak into the oil, leading to engine damage, stalling, and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
The failure of the head gasket can cause coolant to leak into the oil, leading to engine damage, stalling, and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
The stalling and seizure of the engine can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, potentially leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
